Quarter: The fiscal quarter in which the compliance training completion rate is recorded (e.g., Q2 2025).
Completion_Rate: The percentage of employees who completed the compliance training within the specified quarter.
Year: The year in which the compliance training completion data is applicable.
Industry_Average: The average compliance training completion rate in the virtual/remote healthcare industry for the specified quarter.
Compliance_Standard: The specific compliance standard or certification that the training pertains to (e.g., ISO 27001).
